sentences.english: Because of your temple at Jerusalem kings will bring you gifts.
sentences.chinese: 因你耶路撒冷的殿，列王必帶貢物獻給你。

sentences.english: And the LORD's tribute of the sheep was six hundred and threescore and fifteen.
sentences.chinese: 從其中歸耶和華爲貢物的，有六百七十五隻。

sentences.english: Of which the Lord's part was six hundred and seventy-five.
sentences.chinese: 從其中歸耶和華爲貢物的，有六百七十五隻。

sentences.english: Because of thy temple at Jerusalem shall kings bring presents unto thee.
sentences.chinese: 因你耶路撒冷的殿，列王必帶貢物獻給你。

sentences.english: of which the tribute for the LORD was 675;
sentences.chinese: 從其中歸耶和華爲貢物的，有六百七十五隻。
